IBADAN – Former Senate Leader and the lawmaker representing Oyo Central Senatorial District, Senator Teslim Folarin has felicitated Vice President Yemi Osinbajo, on his 65th birthday, saying he is an epitome of loyalty and patriotism. The Chairman Senate Committee on Local Content, in his goodwill message to the acting president, stated that Vice President Yemi Osinbajo remained a typical example of a God-fearing, loyal, dedicated, committed and patriotic public administrator. The message read in parts: “On behalf of my family and the good people of Oyo Central Senatorial District, I extend most sincere congratulations and best wishes to Nigeria Vice-President and acting president, His Excellency Prof. Yemi Osinbajo, SAN, GCON, on the auspicious occasion of his 65th birthday anniversary. Russia/Ukraine: Buhari Okays $8.5m For Evacuation Of Nigerians… 2023: Pro-Osinbajo Group Visits Zulum To Seek Support “Your Excellency’s achievements, impacts and genuine support for President Muhammadu Buhari are huge and indelible. You remain a precious asset to Yorubaland and Nigeria at large. “As your years, so shall your strength. I join your families, friends, world leaders and millions of Nigerians to celebrate you. May excellent character never depart you. Please accept my solemn best wishes, Your Excellency,” he concluded.